## 4) IAM JSON files

### `iam/snowflake_role_trust_policy.json`
(Uses your Snowflake values you already used)

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "SnowflakeAssumeRole",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": {
        "AWS": "arn:aws:iam::053442322070:user/30fe1000-s"
      },
      "Action": "sts:AssumeRole",
      "Condition": {
        "StringEquals": {
          "sts:ExternalId": "SAC77099_SFCRole=2_H8Gn5k/Z1rrfiM5yHWEhkXZ29Wo="
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}